  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/4c1266d0c5c72e394e610d9a6c102bf5.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the story unfold between three roommates who all believe they saw an angel when they were younger. As each girl tries to determine if the angel might be one of the other two, their relationships deepen until the small interactions blossom into love. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Which two will you try to see pair together?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/092db6a0b8006815cc47873fb9384c3b.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=286 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/1308a565e2b63485bfaa063530956a8f.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cute, charming, and sweet moments shared between the girls will bloom into something greater.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/031efab2b5b6ceecd49805dd5591703e.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=1765 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/ee648c3a42c424f415e8921f380e1651.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swap between each heroine's perspective as you progress the story and their relationships.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/f81b3a94b1ae59ad26db9504d5cb8c9d.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=667 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Steam release includes both the original<i> Wanting Wings</i>, and its sequel,<i> Faraway Feathers</i>, so you can enjoy all the epilogues for each pairing, along with a new heroine and her pairing.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/4c1266d0c5c72e394e610d9a6c102bf5.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the story unfold between three roommates who all believe they saw an angel when they were younger. As each girl tries to determine if the angel might be one of the other two, their relationships deepen until the small interactions blossom into love. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Which two will you try to see pair together?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/092db6a0b8006815cc47873fb9384c3b.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=286 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/1308a565e2b63485bfaa063530956a8f.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cute, charming, and sweet moments shared between the girls will bloom into something greater.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/031efab2b5b6ceecd49805dd5591703e.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=1765 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/ee648c3a42c424f415e8921f380e1651.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swap between each heroine's perspective as you progress the story and their relationships.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685610/extras/f81b3a94b1ae59ad26db9504d5cb8c9d.avif?t=1771215767\" width=780 height=667 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Steam release includes both the original<i> Wanting Wings</i>, and its sequel,<i> Faraway Feathers</i>, so you can enjoy all the epilogues for each pairing, along with a new heroine and her pairing.</p>",
